y-bidah-is-misguidance-fire\/","url_meta":{"origin":7669,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Bid&#8217;ah: Every innovation is misguidance in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would praise Allah in his sermon, as He deserves to be praised, and then say, \u201cWhomever Allah guides, no one can lead him astray. Whomever Allah sends astray, no one can guide him. The truest word\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3383,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/16\/tawakkul-hasbuna-allah-wa-nima-wakil-wakeel\/","url_meta":{"origin":7669,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Trust: Abraham and Muhammad rely upon Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Abraham, upon him be peace, said\u00a0when he was thrown into the fire, \u201cAllah is enough for us, and excellent is he as the guardian,\u201d and it was likewise said by Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him, when they said, \u201cVerily, the people have gathered against you,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":236,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/07\/prophet-speaks-to-understand\/","url_meta":{"origin":7669,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Clarity: The Prophet speaks so they understand him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The discourse of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was clear such that he was understood by everyone who heard him. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4839 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0644\u0627\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u0633\u0644\u0645\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/10\/musa-moses-patience-harm\/","url_meta":{"origin":7669,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Musa: Moses hurt by people, but was patient","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was distributing charity when a man from the Ansar said, \u201cBy Allah, Muhammad did not intend to please Allah with this!\u201d I came to the Prophet and told him about it, then anger could be seen on\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2796,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/06\/ibrahim-abraham-best-creation\/","url_meta":{"origin":7669,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ibrahim: Prophet Abraham is best of creation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO best of creation!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat is Abraham, upon him be peace.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2369 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u00a0\u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/24\/prophet-face-like-qamar\/","url_meta":{"origin":7669,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: The Prophet&#8217;s face was like the Moon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ishaq reported: A man asked Al-Bara', may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWas the face of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, like a sword?\u201d Al-Bara' said, \u201cNo, it was like the moon.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3552 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u0633\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0642\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f\